{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342610/extras/Wishlist.png?t=1734476855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Survive by mastering intense combat: slash with your sword, dash and teleport to evade, and blast enemies with flames and electricity. Light is your only source of healing. Recharge within its glow, or brave the shadows for greater rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342610/extras/Vampire.gif?t=1734476855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each wave grows deadlier. Strategize carefully, level up to boost your power, and fight to outlast the darkness.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342610/extras/Zombie.gif?t=1734476855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Key Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survive Horde Combat</strong>: Battle waves of creatures and face unique bosses.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Light vs. Dark</strong>: Stay in the light to recover or risk the shadows for rewards.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Spell-Powered Action</strong>: Dash, teleport, and wield arcane abilities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Immersive Atmosphere</strong>: Gothic visuals and eerie soundscapes set the tone.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342610/extras/Werewolf.gif?t=1734476855\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wishlist today and join our Discord to help bring this game to life!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342610/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734476855","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3342610/page_bg_generated.j